      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. it's definitely deep, the edges are kinda gaping open like i can see the fatty tissue inside. if i use a thick layer of honey, do u think that'll help pull the edges together so i don't need stitches? i'm really trying to avoid the doctor if i can make it work myself.",
